10 years of gratitude and love for the #CMAawards ❤️❤️

After 37 hard hours of labor, finally getting to push, and ending up having an emergency c section and being put under, Forrest Henry Font made his debut. 🤍 Thank you to our incredible medical team at St Thomas Midtown for taking incredible care of us and making a really scary experience as calm and comfortable as possible  for our little family. Forrest is everything Jonah and I could’ve ever dreamed of, and we’d go through it all over again for him 🥹 Thank you Lord for the gift of this perfect boy and this magical time. We are so in love 🤍
We’ve got a one month old 🥹 being your momma is my favorite my sweet Forrest! Dada and i love you so much 🩵

Happy birthday to my rock 🤎 we love you baby! You are the most incredible husband and dada to our little Forrest. 13 years of celebrating birthdays together, and it somehow gets better every year 🥹
